{
	"name": "Edict of Dominion",
	"type": "feature",
	"img": "icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-fist-strike.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": "<p>Your authority radiates like a commandment of flame. You gain proficiency in Persuasion, or if you are already proficient, an expertise die. As an action, you choose a creature within 60 feet that can see or hear you. The creature must succeed on a Charisma Saving Throw (Spellcasting DC) or be [[/condition id=charmed]] until the end of its next turn. While charmed, the creature cannot willingly attack you or target you with harmful abilities or effects. On a success, it takes your proficiency bonus d6 psychic damage as your presence sears their mind.</p>",
